Developer Terms of Use
des: The Salisbury City Helper is designed to provide thorough and comprehensive information to the citizens of, and visitors to the City of Salisbury, Maryland. The skill allows the user to ask questions about services, programs, staff, events and more, answering the question in the most efficient way possible. If the skill is unable to answer the question, the user will be directed to the city website at www.salisbury.md.
priv:
